Interface PwNativeAd.PwNativeAdListener

  • Enclosing class:
    PwNativeAd

    public static interface PwNativeAd.PwNativeAdListener
    Implement this interface to be notified of ad loading events.

      • nativeAdDidFail

        void nativeAdDidFail(PwNativeAd nativeAd,
                     String error)
        This event is fired if the native ad request fails to return an ad.
        Parameters:
        nativeAd - the native ad that failed to load
        error - description of the error that occurred. The error messages are intended to provide information for developers and should not be displayed to the user.
